Package de.wwu.muggl.instructions.general Description

Provides abstract superclasses for the instruction classes. As many insctrutions have a similar functionality and are only distinguished by some particularities, most of their functionality can be re-used. Hence, each instruction inherits a class from this package. Each abstract class inherits either GeneralInstruction or GeneralInstructionWithOtherBytes. GeneralInstructionWithOtherBytes also inherits GeneralInstruction.
